      "comment": "GLORIA KEEPING (6) filled the minor money three on end before breaking through for a deserved win last time, scoring at this track over 520m (29.89). Has a solid record from this box including three wins and a minor placing. Form reads well for this. EUREKA MAC (1) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but had to settle for a minor placing when a neck second over 515m at Gosford, clocking 29.70. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to be in this for a long way. SIR SILVERTREE (8) ran below best last time finishing fifth (30.55) over 515m at Sandown from Box 6. Expected to give a good account. ",
